components.name: ContactCtaComponent
components.templateData:
Web development

We make websites in Angular, Svelte, React, any other JS (or non-js) library, or static HTML. We can integrate with your existing stack, or we can suggest solutions. We offer free (unbilled) consultation, wherein a Blazed Engineer will work with you to find the best solution for your company.

Contact Us

App development

We can make desktop and mobile apps. Desktop can be Macintosh, Windows, and/or Linux. Mobile can be IOS, Android, and/or Windows Phone. Apps specifically refer to installed applications, and usually are more costly and time consuming to produce.

Contact Us

components.templateData:
Our Divisions

Blazed Telecom

We are a telecommunications provider who provides telecom setup and monitoring services, call center management services, and two factor authentication (2FA) verifications services.

Visit Website

Blazed Publishing

We are a publishing company who publishes text (including: books, magazines, newspapers, and scholarly journals), media (including: images, videos, films, music, interactive content), and software (digital assets, source code, release distributables).

Visit Website

Blazed Systems

We are a systems administration company; we manage networks, build software, maintain software, and engineer solutions. Discover the Blazed Systems Edge, you would never imagine what's possible.

Visit Website

Contribute to Blazed software

With the Blazed Development Group, anyone can contribute to Blazed software! We don't just need programmers, we also need testers, designers, project managers, marketers, and sales reps. Any way you can contribute would be most appreciated!

Visit GitHub Facebook Group
